ActAn Act to amend the Tobacco Act and the Non-smokers' Health Act and to make consequential amendments to other Acts
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day that is 200 Days After the Day on which this Order is Made as the Day on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder Fixing the day that is 200 days after the day on which this Order is made as the day on which subsection 7(2), section 8, subsection 11(2) and sections 25, 28, 31 and 57 of AN ACT TO AMEND THE TOBACCO ACT AND THE NON-SMOKERS' HEALTH ACT AND TO MAKE CONSEQUENTIAL AMENDMENTS TO OTHER ACTS, chapter 9 of the Statutes of Canada, 2018, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2019-0021 Publication Date: 2019-05-01
